metadata.title: Gulf of Alaska Acoustic/Trawl Pollock Survey

metadata.description:
Parameter
number and size to pelagic walleye Pollock

Measurement Details
Assessed by echo integration and trawling. Spawning Survey. No survey in 1982.

Geographic Area
Shelikof Strait, Gulf of Alaska

[ A TCODE project ]
